  "detailed_description": "Misfit is a third person shooter, in which you battle over objectives, take down other players, fight waves of enemies, and survive until the portal opens for you to escape.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-fluid third person gameplay<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-A multiplayer game you've never experienced before<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Wide variety of abilities such as Super Speed, Mega Jump, Grenade Launcher, and Giant Mech Armour<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Multiple maps to choose from, including ancient deserts, modern cities and medieval castles",
  "about_the_game": "Misfit is a third person shooter, in which you battle over objectives, take down other players, fight waves of enemies, and survive until the portal opens for you to escape.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-fluid third person gameplay<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-A multiplayer game you've never experienced before<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Wide variety of abilities such as Super Speed, Mega Jump, Grenade Launcher, and Giant Mech Armour<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Multiple maps to choose from, including ancient deserts, modern cities and medieval castles",
